  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Validation results are reported from bench-top experiments and in-vitro loop tests; however, the provenance chain for at least one result is incomplete — the structured generation activity linking the result to its producing experiment is absent from the package.",
