      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples must be characterized for batch-to-batch variability in blood analog properties and hemolysis baseline.",
      "rationale": "Only a single batch of porcine blood was used for in-vitro validation. Batch-to-batch variability was not characterized. Not assessed."
