    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below required thresholds and six factors remaining not assessed, the regulatory submission team accepted the package under a conditional approval pathway pending supplemental validation data. The decision reflects the sponsor's determination that the assessed factors collectively provide sufficient confidence for an Investigational Device Exemption filing, with post-market commitments to address the outstanding epistemic gaps. Note: provenance documentation for the in-vitro hemolysis loop validation result is incomplete; the structured activity record linking the result to its generating experiment was not included in this package version.",
